headline: T Rowe Price (TROW) Q3 2025 Earnings Transcript
summary: On an asset-weighted basis, results were stronger, with 64%, 57%, and 78% of our fund assets beating their peer groups on the three, five, and 10-year basis.  While we have always believed that focusing on the long term is the right lens for investment performance, I want to call out improvement in our one-year numbers, with 53% of fund assets now beating their peer groups.
